OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FThis is about power - those who have
OL,7,Fit and those who don't.
OL,9,FThose who are given the benefit of the
OL,10,Fdoubt and those who are ignored.
OL,12,FThose believed and those not.
OL,14,FGrenfell is the greatest housing
OL,15,Ftragedy in modern British history.
OL,17,FPeople died in a tower block in the
OL,18,Ffifth richest country in the world, in
OL,19,Fits capital city dripping with wealth.
