OL,3,CA divide in power: How Grenfell
OL,4,Cexposed Britain's social housing crisis
OL,6,FThe deeply uncomfortable truth is
OL,7,Fpeople with power did not do enough to
OL,8,Fstop it from happening for years,
OL,9,Fmultiple times. Call it missed
OL,10,Fopportunity, call it oversight, call
OL,11,Fit complicated, call it neglect.
OL,13,FWho cared enough to listen to social
OL,14,Fhousing tenants when they reported
OL,15,Fproblems over and over and over?
OL,17,FWho cared enough to make sure the
OL,18,Fmaterial being used to house them
OL,19,Fwouldn't kill them?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
